The paper discusses a tagging system for blockchains that can be used for e-crime investigations and privacy research. This suggests that the paper could belong to the categories of computer security (cs.CR), databases (cs.DB), cybercrime (cs.CY), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and software engineering (cs.SE).
